title: Girl compares 11 dressing room mirrors to show how different they make her look (12 HQ Photos)
text:
View as Slideshow 1 
Retail stores will do whatever it takes to get you to buy their products, so of course they’re going to try anything to make you look really good while you’re trying on their clothing. 
However, it’s kind of shocking to see the comparison of a girl hanging out in her house and what she “looks like” in these dressing rooms. 
This is Inna, before she set out on her tour of stores… 2 
…and this is what she looks like in the H&M dressing room. Crazy, right? Check out the ten other stores she went to and how her face and body change in each one. 3
